The installations procedures are the default for GNU programs:
tar -zxvf uspds-version.tar.gz (by version, understand the version of the program).
cd uspds-version
./configure
make
make install (this step is deprecated)

For any error in compilation, be sure that your system have installed all required softwares and libraries. If you continues to get errors please, send an email to dmelo87@gmail.com.
